# Cloudflare Pages Global Headers
# Applied to all routes served by Cloudflare Pages (static files + Functions API).
#
# X-Robots-Tag: Prevents search engines from indexing, following links, caching,
#               or showing snippets from any page. This is a data API, not a website.
# X-Content-Type-Options: Prevents browsers from MIME-sniffing the response away
#                         from the declared Content-Type, mitigating XSS vectors.

/*
  X-Robots-Tag: noindex, nofollow, noarchive, nosnippet
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
